{"tid":2129886,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港電台：科頓稱奴隸制是「必要之惡」引起批評","createTime":"2020-07-29T02:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T02:20:07.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02e5a2fe70aebe8411bcf9ff5f493f9b870c28b1","tid":2129886,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"《環看天下》： 科頓稱奴隸制是「必要之惡」引起批評<br />\n2020-07-29 HKT 09:52<br />\n美國共和參議員科頓近日提到奴隸制度是美國立國的「必要之惡」引起批評。<br />\n<br />\n他早前提出立法，反對聯邦撥款資助《紐約時報》雜誌發起的「1619項目」編入中學課程。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》認為，「1619項目」是反思奴隸制歷史，以及讓大眾了解奴隸制至今的影響，以及非裔美國人的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540501-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540501-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=bad88173\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540501-20200729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=922232c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540501-20200729.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}